sentences: Gisburg (born in 1966 as Gisburg Smialek) is an Austrian Composer, Singer and Music Editor for Film.
She moved to New York City in 1992 and performed around the Knitting factory and Roulette scene.
She was a member of the Chinese Hai-Tien choir with Mrs. Pi-Chu Hsiao for 6 years, and recorded with Gary Lucas Chinese pop music of the 1930s and 1950s.
